Choe3-ko E5 Chhi3-giam7
Chu2 Ia5-sou bat 3 pai2 mng7 Pi2-tek kong2: “Li2 thiaN3 Goa2 mah?” Lan2 tioh8 khoaN3 chit-e5 choe3 choe3-ko e5 chhi3-giam7. Che si7 beh chhi3-giam7 lang5 tui3 Chu2 Ia5-sou u7 khian5-seng5, jiat8-sim, chin7-tiong a2-bo5? Li2 siuN7 kiam2 u7 pi2 chit-e5 koh-khah tiong7-iau3 e5 chhi3-giam7 mah?
Kau3 kin-a2-jit8, lan2 iau2-ku2 khoaN3 che choe3 lan2 siok8-leng5 seng-oah8 choe3-ko e5 chhi3-giam7; chit e5 chhi3-giam7 u7 pau-ham5 i2-ha7 saN-tiam2.
1. Choe3 Chu2 E5 Hak8-seng Choe3-ko E5 Chhi3-giam7
Lek8-tai7 i2-lai5, Ia5-sou Ki-tok ai3 lang5 sun7-hok8 siok8 ti7 I; m7 si7 chhut-ti7 bian2-kiong2, kiaN-hiaN5; oan5-choan5 si7 chhut ti7 thiaN3. Sat-tan3 kam-goan7 chiong thiN-e7 ban7-kok kap in e5 eng5-kng hou7 Ia5-sou chai-iaN2 ThiN-pe7 e5 chi2-i3 choat8-tui3 m7-si7 bian2-kiong2 lang5 sun7-hok8 I, I chi2-u7 in2-chhoa7, m7 bat kiong5-pek. lang5 tek-khak tioh8 chiau3 ka-ki7 e5 i3-chi3 lai5 soan2-tek8 Ia5-sou; tioh8 hou7 I e5 thiaN3 sou2 kam2-hoa3 in2-chhoa7 lai5 sun7-hok8 I. Chit khoan2 e5 kiat-hap8, pi2 eng7 kiong5-pek hou7 lang5 hang5-hok8 khah chhin-bit8, u7 khui3-lat8, oe7 chun5-chai7 koh-khah ku2. In-ui7 thiaN3 e5 ian5-kou3, Ia5-sou Ki-tok lai5 kau3 chit se3-kan. ThiaN3------hou7 I ui7-tioh8 tim5-lun5 e5 jin5-lui7 lai5 si2. ThiaN3------chiah oe7 in2-chhoa7 jin5-lui7 lai5 kau3 I e5 bin7-cheng5. Kiam2 u7 sim2-mih8 kiat-iok e5 soan-se3, pi2 chit-ku3 kan2-tan e5 chhi3-giam7 “Li2 thiaN3 Goa2 mah?” koh-khah u7 khui3-lat8?
I long2 bo5 eng7 pat8 e5 bun7-toe5------chhin-chhiuN7 kau3-gi7, sin3-tiau5, sin5-hak8 lai5 mng7 Pi2-tek, ia7 bo5 kong2-khi2 choe7, hoan2-hoe2 a2-si7 ui7 Chu2 choe3-kang e5 su7; I chi2-u7 mng7 chit8 e5 bun7-toe5 “Li2 thiaN3 Goa2 mah?” Hit-si5 chiu7-si7 Chu2 Ia5-sou beh ka3-si7 hak8-seng choe3-au7 koh si7 choe3 ho2 e5 ki-hoe7, in-ui7 I bo5 ku2 chiu7 beh li7-khui in. I pun2-lai5 oe7 thang kong2-khi2 choe3 hak8-seng e5 chu-keh, sin3-tiau5, kau3-hoe7 chou-chit, chong2-si7 I long2 bo5 kong2 chiah-e5, chi2-u7 kong2 “Li2 thiaN3 Goa2 mah?”; in-ui7 chit-ku3 u7 pau-ham5 it-chhe3; kun-pun2 e5 bun7-toe5 na7 kai2-koat, pat8 e5 bun7-toe5 chu7-jian5 chiu7 oe7 kai2-koat.
Kin-a2-jit8 kau3-hoe7 lai7 u7 chheng-chheng ban7-ban7 e5 sin3-tou5 chin oah8-tang7, ia7 u7 chin-choe7 gi7-kang. Chong2-si7 in ko3-jin5 tui3 Ia5-sou Ki-tok bo5 thiaN3-sim. Kan-ta u7 tian2-le2 kap gi5-sek iau2 bo5 kau3-giah8; tiong-sit8 ti7 sin3-giong2 e5 ki-pun2 bun7-toe5, ia7 boe7 oe7 cheng3-beng5 ti7 li2 e5 sim-lai7 khak-sit8 u7 thiaN3 Ia5-sou. U7 chin-choe7 lang5 , in e5 li2-lun7 si7 tioh8, chong2-si7 in e5 sim si7 chho3-gou7. In-ui7 an2-ni, hian7-tai7 e5 kau3-phai3 chiah u7 hiah choe7 e5 mau5-tun2 kap put-an. Siong7-te3 sou2 siuN2-su3 hou7 lan2 koah tiu7-a2 e5 khi3-ku7, m7-si7 beh eng7 lai5 tui3-hu3 lan2 e5 hiaN-ti7, si7 beh eng7 lai5 siu-koah ngou2-kok. Chin u7 kho2-leng5, ui7-tioh8 sin3-giong2 lai5 sun5-to7--e5, bo5 it-teng7 si7 thiaN3 Ia5-sou. Tu2-tu2 chhin-chhiuN7 Po2-lo5 sou2 kong2: “Goa2 siat-su2......hian3 goa2 e5 seng-khu hou7 he2 sio na7 bo5 jin5-ai3, chiu7 goa2 bo5 tit-tioh8 li7-ek.”
2. Choe3 Chu2 E5 Hak8-seng Phin2-keh Choe3-ko E5 Chhi3-giam7
Tui3 se3-kan but8-chit e5 thai3-tou7, u7 chin-choe7 lang5 an2-ni kong2: An2-ni choe3 kiam2 u7 m7 tioh8? An2-ni choe3 si7 hoan7 choe7 mah? Chit chiong2 ku7 e5 bun7-toe5 goa2 bo5 su-iau3 koh the5-khi2. Lan2 kan-ta eng7 che choe3-ko e5 chhi3-giam7 lai5 kam3-chhat lan2 it-chhe3 e5 heng5-tong7 chiu7 ho2. Che chiaN5-choe3 siok8-leng5 pit8-sia5 kui-cheng3 e5 khui3-lat8. Bun7-toe5 m7-si7 hong3-chhiong3 ti7 u7 bun7-toe5 e5 gu5-lok8, si7 tioh8 a2 m7-tioh8. Chit8 e5 lang5 hou7 Seng3 Sin5 chhiong-moa2 koh sim-lai7 u7 Ki-tok e5 thiaN3, i it-teng7 si7 ai3 beh hok8-sai7 hit ui7 i2-keng tit-tioh8 i e5 sim e5 Chu2, koh ai3 si5-siong5 hou7 I hoaN-hi2, i choat8-tui3 bo5 sim-cheng5 khi3 hoan7-choe7, khi3 thiaN3 se3-kan, khi3 tui-kiu5 choe7-ok tiong e5 khoai3-lok8. Bo5 lang5 oe7 siong-hai7 i ka-ki7 sou2 thiaN3 e5 lang5 ; sou2-i2 bun7-toe5 si7 chai7-ti7 thiaN3------choe3-ko e5 chhi3-giam7.
Chit8 e5 thiaN3 Chu2 e5 lang5 it-teng7 oe7 si5-siong5 ai3 beh hou7 I hoaN-hi2, hou7 I sim-moa2 i3-chiok, an2-ni se3-kan tui3 i chiu7 bo5 koh u7 khip-in2-lat8, i boe7 koh-chai3 him-bou7 se3-kan e5 but8-chit kap khoai3-lok8; in-ui7 Ia5-sou chiaN5-choe3 i e5 it-chhe3. Tui3 an2-ni, leng5-seng3 hong-bin7 thang tit-tioh8 I e5 iuN2-chhi7, kap I saN-kap toa3, ti7 I lai7-bin7, thiaN3 I, chun I choe3 li2 sim-lai7 e5 Ong5; li2 na7 sit8-chai7 thiaN3 I, it-chhe3 e5 bun7-toe5 chiu7 long2 chin ho2 kai2-koat.
3. Choe3 Chu2 E5 Hak8-seng Hok8-sai7 Chu2 Choe3-ko E5 Chhi3-giam7
Choe3 Chu2 e5 hak8-seng hok8-sai7 Chu2, si7 in-ui7 thiaN3 I, m7 si7 ui7-tioh8 gi7-bu7. OaN7 oe7 lai5 kong2, m7 si7 ui7-tioh8 chin7 chek-jim7, si7 thiaN3 e5 chhui-pek. Si7 sim2-mih8 lek8-liong7 hou7 Pou3 Tai7-pit8 (ti7 Bi2-kok Ang5-hoan choe3 soan-kau3-su, David Brainerd) goan7-i3 khi3 kau3 bo5 lang5 kiaN5 kau3 e5 khong3-ia2 tui3 In3-te7-an lang5 thoan5 to7-li2? Si7 sim2-mih8 hou7 i ti7 24 he3 e5 si5, chiu7 li7-khui ka-teng5, ka-ki7 chit8-e5 toa3 ti7 bo5 lang5 sou2 kau3 e5 lai7-toe7 chhiu7-na5 lai7? I sui-jian5 hoan7 tioh8 chin giam5-tiong7 e5 hi3-piN7, chong2-si7 i kam-goan7 thun-lun2 iau-go7, khia5 be2 kau3 chin hng7 e5 sou2-chai7, am3-si5 ia3-sian7 koh bo5 ui7 thang hioh-khun3, u7-si5 ti7 chhiu7-na5 lai7 tu2-tioh8 toa7-hou7 lam5 e5 kan-khou2, chong2-si7 i chit8 geh8-jit8 koh chit8 geh8-jit8 thun-lun2 loh8-khi3. I e5 bok8-tek si7 ui7-tioh8 beh hou7 i sou2 thiaN3 e5 In3-te7-an lang5 beng5-pek8 Siong7-te3 thiaN3 in koh chiong I tok8-siN e5 KiaN2 siuN2-su3 in ui7-tioh8 in lai5 si2. Tau3-te2 si7 tui3 to2-ui7 lai5 e5 khui3-lat8 hou7 i thun-lun2 kan-lan5, thong3-khou2? Choat8-tui3 m7-si7 chek-jim7 e5 bun7-toe5, che si7 thiaN3 kam2-tong7 sou2 piau2-hian7 e5. Pou3 Tai7-pit8 thiaN3 i e5 Chu2, sou2-i2 i u7 choe3-ko e5 piau2-hian7.
Chhin-chhiuN7 Ia5 Tek-sun, Li2-un-su-teng, Ma2 Le2-sun3, Te3 Tek-seng, Khek-le2 kap cha2-cheng5 sou2 u7 ui2-tai7 e5 soan-kau3-su ia7 long2 si7 an2-ni. Siat-su2 li2 na7 chin7 sim thiaN3 chu2, li2 ia7 it-teng7 oe7 an2-ni khi3 choe3. Li2 tioh8 eng7 hoaN-hi2 e5 sim hok8-sai7 Chu2, eng7 an2-ni lai5 cheng3-beng5 li2 u7 thiaN3 I. In-ui7 li2 u7 thiaN3 Chu2, sou2-i2 na7 u7 su-iau3 li2 beh ui7 I pang3-sak siN3-mia7, li2 iah8 it-teng7 oe7 hoaN-hi2 kam-goan7 khi3 choe3.
Oh! Chu2 e5 thiaN3-thang3 kap lin5-bin2 e5 sim, hit e5 tng5, khoah, koaiN5, chhim, si7 boe7 thang chhek-tok8 e5. ThiaN3 e5 tui-kiu5 si7 thiaN3 e5 in3-tap, i2-goa7 bo5 pat8 mih8 oe7 boan2-chiok thiaN3 e5 sim. Chu2 Ia5-sou eng7 chiah-nih toa7 e5 thiaN3-thang3 thiaN3 lan2, lan2 na7 bo5 an2-ni thiaN3 I, i2-goa7 bo5 pat8 mih8 oe7 boan2-chiok I e5 sim. Teh chhiat-chhiat him-bou7 thiaN3 e5 lang5 , khoaN3 chai5-po2, chhu3-theh8, chhan5-hng5, long2 m7-si7 tiong7-iau3; chi2-u7 an2-ni thiaN3 Chu2, chiah oe7 tit-tioh8 Ki-tok e5 hoaN-hi2 kap chiap-lap8. Sou2-i2 Chu2 Ia5-sou kong2: “Li2 thiaN3 Goa2 mah?”, chit ku3 chiu7 chiaN5-choe3 mui2 chit8 e5 Ki-tok-tou5 choe3-ko e5 chhi3-giam7.
Ti7 Hoat-kok u7 chit8 e5 chin ho2-giah8 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 , oan3-than3 i e5 tiong7-hu tui3 i leng2-tam7. I e5 tiong7-hu kong2: Li2 iau2 beh tih8 sim2-mih8? Goa2 sou2-u7 e5 chiN5-gun5 long2 kau hou7 li2 koan2, ke-he2 chhu3-theh8 long2-si7 li2 e5, li2 ti7 chia u7 thang chiah8, u7 thang eng7, li2 iau2 teh oan3-than3 sim2-mih8 ah? Hit e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2: Goa2 ai3 tit-tioh8 li2 e5 sim, goa2 ai3 li2 thiaN3 goa2. Hit e5 choe3 tiong7-hu e5 toa7-siaN tui3 i kong2: Boe7 eng7 tit, in-ui7 goa2 e5 sim si7 siok8 ti7 pat8-lang5 --e5, li2 thang tit-tioh8 goa2 e5 it-chhe3, na7-si7 goa2 e5 sim, goa2 e5 thiaN3, li2 bo5 hun7.
Lan2 thang chiong sou2-u7 long2-chong2 hian3 hou7 Chu2, na7-si7 I iau2-boe7 boan2-chiok; in-ui7 thiaN3 teh tui-kiu5 thiaN3 e5 in3-tap, bo5 u7 pat8-mih8 oe7 thang thoe3-oaN7. Hian7-kim I iau2 teh ng3-bang7 li2 in3-tap chit e5 choe3-ko e5 chhi3-giam7-------“Li2 thiaN3 Goa2 mah?”
Siat-su2 kin-a2-jit8 Ia5-sou hian2-hian7 ti7 lan2 tiong-kan, I beh mng7 lan2 tak8-lang5 kong2: “Li2 thiaN3 Goa2 mah?” Lan2 beh chaiN2-iuN7 in3-tap? Lan2 si7 beh siam2-pi7 I e5 chit-bun7, a2-si7 beh kap I kong2 lan2 thiaN3 I? Su3-tou5 Iok-han7 ti7 i e5 phoe kong2: “Goan2 thiaN3 I.” Li2 u7 thiaN3 I a2-bo5? Goa2 u7 thiaN3 I mah?
